Titolo: Legend of Kay

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Legend of Kay is an action-adventure and platforming video game for the PlayStation 2 by German developer Neon Studios about a young anthropomorphic cat warrior named Kay who fights to save his once-peaceful island from the gorillas and rats who have conquered it.
The game received positive reviews to the point a version of the game was developed for the Nintendo DS by Firehazard Studio. It was released on May 28, 2010 in Europe, in North America on June 14, and in Australia on August 26. However, this version did not receive positive reviews.
There were also PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 versions of the game released digitally in Worldwide, featuring improved graphics.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: 63
